                            <h5 class="card-title text-dark">FACULTY OF EDUCATION </h5>
                            <hr>
                            <p class="card-text text-success">
                                The Faculty of Education focuses on shaping future educators and professionals in the field of education.
                                Through innovative teaching methods and practical experiences, students gain a deep understanding of pedagogy, curriculum development, and educational psychology, preparing them to make a positive impact in classrooms.
                            </p>
                            <div class="mt-9">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark">Learn More</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a asp-action="Create" asp-controller="Application" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm mt-3">Apply Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
